CONTACT_FORM_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Have a question or need support? We're here to help!
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food Delivery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants, allowing you to browse menus, place orders, and track your delivery in real-time. Simply select your items, choose your payment method, and wait for your delicious meal to arrive at your doorstep.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What are the delivery fees and estimated delivery times?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant and your location. Estimated delivery times are provided for each order and typically range from 30-60 minutes. You can view all fees and estimated delivery times before confirming your order.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I customize my order or leave special instructions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! You can customize your order by adding special instructions or requests for each item. There's also a section for general delivery instructions where you can provide additional information for the restaurant or delivery driver.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if there's an issue with my order or delivery?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: If you experience any issues with your order or delivery, our customer support team is available 24/7 through the app. You can also track your order in real-time and communicate directly with your delivery driver if needed.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our food delivery service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food delivery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to browse local restaurants, select your favorite dishes, and place an order for delivery. Once confirmed, a nearby driver will pick up your food and bring it straight to your doorstep.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on the restaurant's distance and current demand. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for frequent users that includes free delivery on eligible orders.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on the restaurant's preparation time and the driver's distance. You can track your order in real-time through the app to get a more accurate estimate.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order in advance?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply select your desired delivery time during checkout, and we'll make sure your food arrives fresh at the specified time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please use the 'Help' section in the app to report the issue. Our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you and ensure your satisfaction.
